name: Eye By Feeling
description:
A series of collages based on our search for perfection in the human form. From photo filters, to diets, to cosmetic surgery, is there anything off limits?

As we preen and pluck away at our flesh, we lose pieces of ourselves in the process while circling around for our next fix. What's next on the menu of physical perfection? Biomechanical implants? Gene editing?

EYE BY FEELING, gene editing to create designer babies.

Collage by @dehiscenceart from my "Skin We Live In Series"
Animation & Audio by @Helldreamer00
Mp4 14.6 MB, 22 sec loop with audio.
